 yet, but I just pushed a version to GitHub which <strong>adds image lazy loading to Autoptimize</strong>;<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Selection_133.jpg\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-10788 alignleft\" src=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Selection_133-1024x419.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"256\" srcset=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Selection_133-1024x419.jpg 1024w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Selection_133-300x123.jpg 300w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Selection_133-624x255.jpg 624w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Selection_133.jpg 1169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 625px) 100vw, 625px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The actual lazy-loading is implemented by the integrated <a href=\"https://github.com/aFarkas/lazysizes\">lazysizes JS lazy loader</a> which has a lot of options some of which I will experiment with and bring to Autoptimize to the default improve user experience.</p>\n<p>If you want you can <a href=\"https://github.com/futtta/autoptimize/archive/beta.zip\">download the beta (2.5.0-beta2) now from Github</a> (disable 2.4.4 before activating the beta) and start using the new functionality immediately. And if you have feedback; shoot, I&#8217;ll be happy to take your remarks with me to bring AO 2.5 ready for release (I&#8217;m targeting March, but we&#8217;ll see).</p>\n<p>Enjoy the celebrations and have a great 2019!</p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/04/11/autoptimize-2-2-coming-your-way-care-to-test/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Autoptimize 2.2 coming your way, care to test?\">Autoptimize 2.2 coming your way, care to test? </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/05/24/autoptimize-2-4-beta-3-includes-image-optimization/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Autoptimize 2.4 beta 3 includes image optimization!\">Autoptimize 2.4 beta 3 includes image optimization! </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2012/11/06/dipping-below-the-magical-1-second-page-load-time/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Dipping below the magical 1 second page load time\">Dipping below the magical 1 second page load time </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_wordpress/~4/4yaTyXWZ7W0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/12/31/autoptimize-2-5-beta-image-lazy-loading/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"22\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/12/31/autoptimize-2-5-beta-image-lazy-loading/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"How to fix render-blocking jquery.js in Autoptimize\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/futtta_wordpress/~3/38Sd8TKCRg8/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\"